ent-AU14CCAFArmor = ISAS Armor
    .desc = Standard body armor worn by frontline CCAF infantry. This unit has been modified for compatibility with the Integrated Soldier Armor System backpack, which links to a CG982 ISACV to deliver real time combat data. Currently in field trials with select CCAF infantry units.
ent-AU14CCAFArmorPadless = ISAS Padless Armor
    .desc = Standard body armor worn by frontline CCAF infantry. This unit has been modified for compatibility with the Integrated Soldier Armor System backpack, which links to a CG982 ISACV to deliver real time combat data. Currently in field trials with select CCAF infantry units. This unit has had its shoulder pads removed.
ent-AU14CCAFArmorStripped = ISAS Stripped Armor
    .desc = Standard body armor worn by frontline CCAF infantry. This unit has been modified for compatibility with the Integrated Soldier Armor System backpack, which links to a CG982 ISACV to deliver real time combat data. Currently in field trials with select CCAF infantry units. This unit has had its shoulder pads and greaves removed.
